      <section eId="sec_1198_E">
        <num>1198-E</num>
        <heading>Responsibilities of the authority</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1198_E__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The purchase, in the name of the authority, or in the name of any\nmunicipality or municipalities, of any water facility or distribution\nsystem or parts thereof involved in the supply of water to the district;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1198_E__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The operation of any water facility or distribution system or\nparts thereof by any public water suppliers which operate in geographic\nareas adjacent to the district;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1198_E__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The creation of additional water authorities to supply water to\nportions of the district as described in section eleven hundred\nninety-eight-c of this article; and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1198_E__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The retention of the water supply system within the district which\nis in existence as of the effective date of this title.\n  2. Following any purchase pursuant to paragraph</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1198_E__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of subdivision one\nof this section:\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1198_E__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Meter service to its customers; and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1198_E__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Repair and maintain that portion of a water supply pipe extending\nfrom the water mains to the water meter. For purposes of this paragraph\n"water supply pipe" shall mean a pipe or line which connects the water\nmains directly to a customer's water meter.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
